{
  "video_id": "FIrgjCNcDBI",
  "title": "Lian Pin Koh: A drone's-eye view of conservation",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13360.0,
      "end_time": 15292.0,
      "text": "When we think of Nepal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15292.0,
      "end_time": 17747.0,
      "text": "we tend to think of the snow-capped mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17747.0,
      "end_time": 19019.0,
      "text": "of the Himalayas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19019.0,
      "end_time": 22468.0,
      "text": "the crystal-clear still waters of its alpine lakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22468.0,
      "end_time": 25514.0,
      "text": "or the huge expanse of its grasslands."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25514.0,
      "end_time": 27721.0,
      "text": "What some of us may not realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27721.0,
      "end_time": 30045.0,
      "text": "is that in the Himalayan foothills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30045.0,
      "end_time": 32219.0,
      "text": "where the climate is much warmer"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32219.0,
      "end_time": 34307.0,
      "text": "and the landscape much greener,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34307.0,
      "end_time": 36733.0,
      "text": "there lives a great diversity of wildlife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36733.0,
      "end_time": 39469.0,
      "text": "including the one-horned rhinoceros,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39469.0,
      "end_time": 41143.0,
      "text": "the Asian elephant"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41143.0,
      "end_time": 43218.0,
      "text": "and the Bengal tiger."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43218.0,
      "end_time": 45070.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately, these animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45070.0,
      "end_time": 47733.0,
      "text": "are under constant threat from poachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47733.0,
      "end_time": 51045.0,
      "text": "who hunt and kill them for their body parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51045.0,
      "end_time": 53254.0,
      "text": "To stop the killing of these animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53254.0,
      "end_time": 55852.0,
      "text": "battalions of soldiers and rangers"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55852.0,
      "end_time": 59101.0,
      "text": "are sent to protect Nepal&#39;s national parks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59101.0,
      "end_time": 60726.0,
      "text": "but that is not an easy task,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60726.0,
      "end_time": 63397.0,
      "text": "because these soldiers have to patrol"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63397.0,
      "end_time": 66388.0,
      "text": "thousands of hectares of forests on foot"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66388.0,
      "end_time": 68029.0,
      "text": "or elephant backs."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68029.0,
      "end_time": 70514.0,
      "text": "It is also risky for these soldiers"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70514.0,
      "end_time": 72895.0,
      "text": "when they get into gunfights with poachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72895.0,
      "end_time": 74911.0,
      "text": "and therefore Nepal is always looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 74911.0,
      "end_time": 78207.0,
      "text": "for new ways to help with protecting the forests"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78207.0,
      "end_time": 80184.0,
      "text": "and wildlife."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80184.0,
      "end_time": 82693.0,
      "text": "Well recently, Nepal acquired a new tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82693.0,
      "end_time": 85406.0,
      "text": "in the fight against wildlife crime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85406.0,
      "end_time": 87112.0,
      "text": "and these are drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87112.0,
      "end_time": 90386.0,
      "text": "or more specifically, conservation drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90386.0,
      "end_time": 92900.0,
      "text": "For about a year now, my colleagues and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92900.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "have been building drones for Nepal"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 97658.0,
      "text": "and training the park protection personnel"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97658.0,
      "end_time": 99636.0,
      "text": "on the use of these drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99636.0,
      "end_time": 101268.0,
      "text": "Not only does a drone give you"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101268.0,
      "end_time": 103742.0,
      "text": "a bird&#39;s-eye view of the landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103742.0,
      "end_time": 106777.0,
      "text": "but it also allows you to capture detailed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106777.0,
      "end_time": 110759.0,
      "text": "high-resolution images of objects on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110759.0,
      "end_time": 114268.0,
      "text": "This, for example, is a pair of rhinoceros"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114268.0,
      "end_time": 117205.0,
      "text": "taking a cooling bath on a hot summer day"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117205.0,
      "end_time": 119168.0,
      "text": "in the lowlands of Nepal."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119168.0,
      "end_time": 121399.0,
      "text": "Now we believe that drones have"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 121399.0,
      "end_time": 123207.0,
      "text": "tremendous potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123207.0,
      "end_time": 125985.0,
      "text": "not only for combating wildlife crime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 125985.0,
      "end_time": 127948.0,
      "text": "but also for monitoring the health"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 127948.0,
      "end_time": 130487.0,
      "text": "of these wildlife populations."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130487.0,
      "end_time": 132337.0,
      "text": "So what is a drone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132337.0,
      "end_time": 134846.0,
      "text": "Well, the kind of drone I&#39;m talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 134846.0,
      "end_time": 136947.0,
      "text": "is simply a model aircraft"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136947.0,
      "end_time": 139392.0,
      "text": "fitted with an autopilot system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 139392.0,
      "end_time": 143661.0,
      "text": "and this autopilot unit contains a tiny computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143661.0,
      "end_time": 147715.0,
      "text": "a GPS, a compass, a barometric altimeter"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 147715.0,
      "end_time": 149974.0,
      "text": "and a few other sensors."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 149974.0,
      "end_time": 151393.0,
      "text": "Now a drone like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 151393.0,
      "end_time": 153599.0,
      "text": "is meant to carry a useful payload,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153599.0,
      "end_time": 155382.0,
      "text": "such as a video camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155382.0,
      "end_time": 157370.0,
      "text": "or a photographic camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 157370.0,
      "end_time": 160719.0,
      "text": "It also requires a software that allows the user"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160719.0,
      "end_time": 162420.0,
      "text": "to program a mission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162420.0,
      "end_time": 164826.0,
      "text": "to tell the drone where to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164826.0,
      "end_time": 166903.0,
      "text": "Now people I talk to are often surprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166903.0,
      "end_time": 169234.0,
      "text": "when they hear that these are the only"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169234.0,
      "end_time": 172341.0,
      "text": "four components that make a conservation drone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 172341.0,
      "end_time": 173845.0,
      "text": "but they are even more surprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173845.0,
      "end_time": 177345.0,
      "text": "when I tell them how affordable these components are."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177345.0,
      "end_time": 179631.0,
      "text": "The facts is, a conservation drone"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179631.0,
      "end_time": 181890.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t cost very much more than"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181890.0,
      "end_time": 183867.0,
      "text": "a good laptop computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 183867.0,
      "end_time": 187126.0,
      "text": "or a decent pair of binoculars."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187126.0,
      "end_time": 190098.0,
      "text": "So now that you&#39;ve built your own conservation drone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190098.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "you probably want to go fly it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194193.0,
      "text": "but how does one fly a drone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 194193.0,
      "end_time": 195785.0,
      "text": "Well, actually, you don&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 195785.0,
      "end_time": 198275.0,
      "text": "because the drone flies itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198275.0,
      "end_time": 201405.0,
      "text": "All you have to do is to program a mission"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201405.0,
      "end_time": 203665.0,
      "text": "to tell the drone where to fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 203665.0,
      "end_time": 205984.0,
      "text": "But you simply do that by clicking on"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 205984.0,
      "end_time": 209233.0,
      "text": "a few way points on the Google Maps interface"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 209233.0,
      "end_time": 211483.0,
      "text": "using the open-source software."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 211483.0,
      "end_time": 213430.0,
      "text": "Those missions could be as simple"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 213430.0,
      "end_time": 215456.0,
      "text": "as just a few way points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 215456.0,
      "end_time": 218833.0,
      "text": "or they could be slightly longer and more complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 218833.0,
      "end_time": 221254.0,
      "text": "to fly along a river system."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 221254.0,
      "end_time": 225103.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, we fly the drone in a lawnmower-type pattern"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 225103.0,
      "end_time": 227223.0,
      "text": "and take pictures of that area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 227223.0,
      "end_time": 229194.0,
      "text": "and those pictures can be processed"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 229194.0,
      "end_time": 231933.0,
      "text": "to produce a map of that forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 231933.0,
      "end_time": 234536.0,
      "text": "Other researchers might want to fly the drone"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234536.0,
      "end_time": 236678.0,
      "text": "along the boundaries of a forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236678.0,
      "end_time": 238849.0,
      "text": "to watch out for poachers or people"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 238849.0,
      "end_time": 241767.0,
      "text": "who might be trying to enter the forest illegally."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 241767.0,
      "end_time": 243647.0,
      "text": "Now whatever your mission is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 243647.0,
      "end_time": 245120.0,
      "text": "once you&#39;ve programmed it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 245120.0,
      "end_time": 248103.0,
      "text": "you simply upload it to the autopilot system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 248103.0,
      "end_time": 249743.0,
      "text": "bring your drone to the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 249743.0,
      "end_time": 252958.0,
      "text": "and launch it simply by tossing it in the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 252958.0,
      "end_time": 255300.0,
      "text": "And often we&#39;ll go about this mission"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 255300.0,
      "end_time": 258360.0,
      "text": "taking pictures or videos along the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 258360.0,
      "end_time": 260294.0,
      "text": "and usually at that point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 260293.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262511.0,
      "text": "we will go grab ourselves a cup of coffee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 262511.0,
      "end_time": 265441.0,
      "text": "sit back, and relax for the next few minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 265441.0,
      "end_time": 268952.0,
      "text": "although some of us sit back and panic for the next few minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 268952.0,
      "end_time": 271170.0,
      "text": "worrying that the drone will not return."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271170.0,
      "end_time": 273443.0,
      "text": "Usually it does, and when it does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 273443.0,
      "end_time": 276849.0,
      "text": "it even lands automatically."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 276849.0,
      "end_time": 279756.0,
      "text": "So what can we do with a conservation drone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 279756.0,
      "end_time": 283149.0,
      "text": "Well, when we built our first prototype drone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 283149.0,
      "end_time": 285667.0,
      "text": "our main objective was to fly it over"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285667.0,
      "end_time": 289556.0,
      "text": "a remote rainforest in North Sumatra, Indonesia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 289556.0,
      "end_time": 292605.0,
      "text": "to look for the nest of a species of great ape"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 292605.0,
      "end_time": 294761.0,
      "text": "known as the orangutan."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 294761.0,
      "end_time": 297417.0,
      "text": "The reason we wanted to do that was because"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 297417.0,
      "end_time": 299446.0,
      "text": "we needed to know how many individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 299446.0,
      "end_time": 302833.0,
      "text": "of this species are still left in that forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 302833.0,
      "end_time": 305019.0,
      "text": "Now the traditional method of surveying"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 305019.0,
      "end_time": 308621.0,
      "text": "for orangutans is to walk the forest on foot"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 308621.0,
      "end_time": 310508.0,
      "text": "carrying heavy equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 310508.0,
      "end_time": 314158.0,
      "text": "and to use a pair of binoculars to look up in the treetops"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 314158.0,
      "end_time": 317576.0,
      "text": "where you might find an orangutan or its nest."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 317576.0,
      "end_time": 319302.0,
      "text": "Now as you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 319302.0,
      "end_time": 322272.0,
      "text": "that is a very time-consuming, labor-intensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 322272.0,
      "end_time": 323990.0,
      "text": "and costly process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 323990.0,
      "end_time": 325786.0,
      "text": "so we were hoping that drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 325786.0,
      "end_time": 329111.0,
      "text": "could significantly reduce the cost of surveying"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 329111.0,
      "end_time": 331678.0,
      "text": "for orangutan populations in Indonesia"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 331678.0,
      "end_time": 334145.0,
      "text": "and elsewhere in Southeast Asia."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 334145.0,
      "end_time": 336500.0,
      "text": "So we were very excited when we captured"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 336500.0,
      "end_time": 339670.0,
      "text": "our first pair of orangutan nests on camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 339670.0,
      "end_time": 342834.0,
      "text": "And this is it; this is the first ever picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 342834.0,
      "end_time": 345874.0,
      "text": "of orangutan nests taken with a drone."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 345874.0,
      "end_time": 347898.0,
      "text": "Since then we have taken pictures"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 347898.0,
      "end_time": 349516.0,
      "text": "of dozens of these nests"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 349516.0,
      "end_time": 352285.0,
      "text": "from around various parts of Southeast Asia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 352285.0,
      "end_time": 354528.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re now working with computer scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 354528.0,
      "end_time": 358447.0,
      "text": "to develop algorithms that can automatically count"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 358447.0,
      "end_time": 360464.0,
      "text": "the number of nests from the thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 360464.0,
      "end_time": 363583.0,
      "text": "of photos we&#39;ve collected so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 363583.0,
      "end_time": 365541.0,
      "text": "But nests are not the only objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 365541.0,
      "end_time": 367331.0,
      "text": "these drones can detect."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 367331.0,
      "end_time": 369640.0,
      "text": "This is a wild orangutan"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 369640.0,
      "end_time": 372161.0,
      "text": "happily feeding on top of a palm tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 372161.0,
      "end_time": 375713.0,
      "text": "seemingly oblivious to our drone that was flying overhead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 375713.0,
      "end_time": 378097.0,
      "text": "not once but several times."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 378097.0,
      "end_time": 381115.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve also taken pictures of other animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 381115.0,
      "end_time": 384236.0,
      "text": "including forest buffalos in Gabon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 384236.0,
      "end_time": 387451.0,
      "text": "elephants, and even turtle nests."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 387451.0,
      "end_time": 390991.0,
      "text": "But besides taking pictures of just the animals themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 390991.0,
      "end_time": 394992.0,
      "text": "we also take pictures of the habitats these animals live in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 394992.0,
      "end_time": 396606.0,
      "text": "because we want to keep track"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 396606.0,
      "end_time": 399560.0,
      "text": "of the health of these habitats."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 399560.0,
      "end_time": 401779.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, we zoom out a little"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 401779.0,
      "end_time": 404032.0,
      "text": "and look at other things that might be happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 404032.0,
      "end_time": 405496.0,
      "text": "in the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 405496.0,
      "end_time": 408796.0,
      "text": "This is an oil palm plantation in Sumatra."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 408796.0,
      "end_time": 412038.0,
      "text": "Now oil palm is a major driver of deforestation"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 412038.0,
      "end_time": 413560.0,
      "text": "in that part of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 413560.0,
      "end_time": 416617.0,
      "text": "so we wanted to use this new drone technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 416617.0,
      "end_time": 419732.0,
      "text": "to keep track of the spread of these plantations"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 419732.0,
      "end_time": 421742.0,
      "text": "in Southeast Asia."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 421742.0,
      "end_time": 424105.0,
      "text": "But drones could also be used to keep track of"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 424105.0,
      "end_time": 426589.0,
      "text": "illegal logging activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 426589.0,
      "end_time": 429030.0,
      "text": "This is a recently logged forest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 429030.0,
      "end_time": 430385.0,
      "text": "again in Sumatra."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 430385.0,
      "end_time": 432544.0,
      "text": "You could even still see the processed"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 432544.0,
      "end_time": 436172.0,
      "text": "wooden planks left on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 436172.0,
      "end_time": 438461.0,
      "text": "But perhaps the most exciting part"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 438461.0,
      "end_time": 441027.0,
      "text": "about taking pictures from the air is"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 441027.0,
      "end_time": 443453.0,
      "text": "we could later stitch these pictures together"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 443453.0,
      "end_time": 446316.0,
      "text": "using special software to create a map"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 446316.0,
      "end_time": 449083.0,
      "text": "of the entire landscape, and this map"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 449083.0,
      "end_time": 451098.0,
      "text": "gives us crucial information"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 451098.0,
      "end_time": 453366.0,
      "text": "for monitoring land use change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 453366.0,
      "end_time": 457113.0,
      "text": "to let us know where and when plantations might be expanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 457113.0,
      "end_time": 459390.0,
      "text": "where forests might be contracting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 459390.0,
      "end_time": 462772.0,
      "text": "or where fires might be breaking out."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 462772.0,
      "end_time": 465004.0,
      "text": "Aerial images could also be processed"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 465004.0,
      "end_time": 467313.0,
      "text": "to produce three-dimensional"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 467313.0,
      "end_time": 469310.0,
      "text": "computer models of forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 469310.0,
      "end_time": 472263.0,
      "text": "Now these models are not just visually appealing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 472263.0,
      "end_time": 474764.0,
      "text": "but they are also geometrically accurate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 474764.0,
      "end_time": 477541.0,
      "text": "which means researchers can now measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 477541.0,
      "end_time": 479666.0,
      "text": "the distance between trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 479666.0,
      "end_time": 482961.0,
      "text": "calculate surface area, the volume of vegetation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 482961.0,
      "end_time": 486160.0,
      "text": "and so on, all of which are important information"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 486160.0,
      "end_time": 489473.0,
      "text": "for monitoring the health of these forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 489473.0,
      "end_time": 491926.0,
      "text": "Recently, we&#39;ve also begun experimenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 491926.0,
      "end_time": 493990.0,
      "text": "with thermal imaging cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 493990.0,
      "end_time": 495879.0,
      "text": "Now these cameras can detect"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 495879.0,
      "end_time": 497864.0,
      "text": "heat-emitting objects from the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 497864.0,
      "end_time": 505236.0,
      "text": "and therefore they are very useful for detecting poachers or their campfires at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 505236.0,
      "end_time": 507120.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve told you quite a lot about"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 507120.0,
      "end_time": 509336.0,
      "text": "what conservation drones are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 509336.0,
      "end_time": 511653.0,
      "text": "how you might operate one of these drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 511653.0,
      "end_time": 513662.0,
      "text": "and what a drone could do for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 513662.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515898.00000000006,
      "text": "I will now tell you where conservation drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 515898.0,
      "end_time": 518353.0,
      "text": "are being used around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 518352.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521405.99999999994,
      "text": "We built our first prototype drones in Switzerland."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 521405.99999999994,
      "end_time": 523546.99999999994,
      "text": "We brought a few of these to Indonesia"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 523547.0,
      "end_time": 525690.0,
      "text": "for the first few test flights."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 525690.0,
      "end_time": 527505.0,
      "text": "Since then, we&#39;ve been building drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 527505.0,
      "end_time": 530187.0,
      "text": "for our collaborators from around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 530187.0,
      "end_time": 532367.0,
      "text": "and these include fellow biologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 532367.0,
      "end_time": 536295.0,
      "text": "and partners from major conservation organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 536295.0,
      "end_time": 538585.0,
      "text": "Perhaps the best and most rewarding part"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 538585.0,
      "end_time": 540711.0,
      "text": "about working with these collaborators"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 540711.0,
      "end_time": 542191.0,
      "text": "is the feedback they give us"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 542191.0,
      "end_time": 544834.0,
      "text": "on how to improve our drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 544834.0,
      "end_time": 546965.0,
      "text": "Building drones for us is"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 546965.0,
      "end_time": 549129.0,
      "text": "a constant work in progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 549129.0,
      "end_time": 552206.0,
      "text": "We are constantly trying to improve them in terms of"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 552206.0,
      "end_time": 554820.0,
      "text": "their range, their ruggedness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 554820.0,
      "end_time": 557498.0,
      "text": "and the amount of payload they can carry."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 557498.0,
      "end_time": 559540.0,
      "text": "We also work with collaborators"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 559540.0,
      "end_time": 562827.0,
      "text": "to discover new ways of using these drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 562827.0,
      "end_time": 566107.0,
      "text": "For example, camera traps are a common tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 566107.0,
      "end_time": 570002.0,
      "text": "used by biologists to take pictures of shy animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 570002.0,
      "end_time": 571563.0,
      "text": "hiding in the forests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 571563.0,
      "end_time": 573897.0,
      "text": "but these are motion-activated cameras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 573897.0,
      "end_time": 576538.0,
      "text": "so they snap a picture every time an animal"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 576538.0,
      "end_time": 578210.0,
      "text": "crosses their path."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 578210.0,
      "end_time": 579762.0,
      "text": "But the problem with camera traps"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 579762.0,
      "end_time": 583505.0,
      "text": "is that the researcher has to go back to the forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 583505.0,
      "end_time": 586958.0,
      "text": "every so often to retrieve those images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 586958.0,
      "end_time": 588610.0,
      "text": "and that takes a lot of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 588610.0,
      "end_time": 590444.0,
      "text": "especially if there are dozens"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 590444.0,
      "end_time": 593572.0,
      "text": "or hundreds of these cameras placed in the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 593572.0,
      "end_time": 596383.0,
      "text": "Now a drone could be designed to perform the task"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 596383.0,
      "end_time": 598107.0,
      "text": "much more efficiently."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 598107.0,
      "end_time": 600777.0,
      "text": "This drone, carrying a special sensor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 600777.0,
      "end_time": 603118.0,
      "text": "could be flown over the forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 603118.0,
      "end_time": 605865.0,
      "text": "and remotely download these images"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 605865.0,
      "end_time": 610002.0,
      "text": "from wi-fi–enabled cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 610002.0,
      "end_time": 612139.0,
      "text": "Radio collars are another tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 612139.0,
      "end_time": 614387.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s commonly used by biologists."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 614387.0,
      "end_time": 617054.0,
      "text": "Now these collars are put onto animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 617054.0,
      "end_time": 619855.0,
      "text": "They transmit a radio signal which allows"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 619855.0,
      "end_time": 625002.0,
      "text": "the researcher to track the movements of these animals across the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 625002.0,
      "end_time": 627659.0,
      "text": "But the traditional way of tracking animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 627659.0,
      "end_time": 629881.0,
      "text": "is pretty ridiculous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 629881.0,
      "end_time": 632825.0,
      "text": "because it requires the researcher to be walking"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 632825.0,
      "end_time": 636939.0,
      "text": "on the ground carrying a huge and cumbersome radio antenna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 636939.0,
      "end_time": 639812.0,
      "text": "not unlike those old TV antennae we used to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 639812.0,
      "end_time": 642780.0,
      "text": "on our rooftops. Some of us still do."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 642780.0,
      "end_time": 645045.0,
      "text": "A drone could be used to do the same job"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 645045.0,
      "end_time": 646704.0,
      "text": "much more efficiently."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 646704.0,
      "end_time": 648410.0,
      "text": "Why not equip a drone"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 648410.0,
      "end_time": 650413.0,
      "text": "with a scanning radio receiver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 650413.0,
      "end_time": 652407.0,
      "text": "fly that over the forest canopy"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 652407.0,
      "end_time": 653945.0,
      "text": "in a certain pattern"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 653945.0,
      "end_time": 656737.0,
      "text": "which would allow the user or the operator"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 656737.0,
      "end_time": 659319.0,
      "text": "to triangulate the location"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 659319.0,
      "end_time": 662306.0,
      "text": "of these radio-collared animals remotely"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 662306.0,
      "end_time": 665279.0,
      "text": "without having to step foot in the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 665279.0,
      "end_time": 667782.0,
      "text": "A third and perhaps most exciting way"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 667782.0,
      "end_time": 669312.0,
      "text": "of using these drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 669312.0,
      "end_time": 672262.0,
      "text": "is to fly them to a really remote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 672262.0,
      "end_time": 674538.0,
      "text": "never-explored-before rainforest"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 674538.0,
      "end_time": 676362.0,
      "text": "somewhere hidden in the tropics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 676362.0,
      "end_time": 680295.0,
      "text": "and parachute down a tiny spy microphone"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 680295.0,
      "end_time": 682741.0,
      "text": "that would allow us to eavesdrop on the calls"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 682741.0,
      "end_time": 686063.0,
      "text": "of mammals, birds, amphibians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 686063.0,
      "end_time": 690340.0,
      "text": "the Yeti, the Sasquatch, Bigfoot, whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 690340.0,
      "end_time": 692079.0,
      "text": "That would give us biologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 692079.0,
      "end_time": 693965.0,
      "text": "a pretty good idea of what animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 693965.0,
      "end_time": 696515.0,
      "text": "might be living in those forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 696515.0,
      "end_time": 698564.0,
      "text": "And finally, I would like to show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 698564.0,
      "end_time": 701665.0,
      "text": "the latest version of our conservation drone."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 701665.0,
      "end_time": 703804.0,
      "text": "The MAJA drone has a wingspan"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 703804.0,
      "end_time": 705478.0,
      "text": "of about two meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 705478.0,
      "end_time": 707428.0,
      "text": "It weighs only about two kilograms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 707428.0,
      "end_time": 709889.0,
      "text": "but it can carry half its weight."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 709889.0,
      "end_time": 712484.0,
      "text": "It is a fully autonomous system."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 712484.0,
      "end_time": 714871.0,
      "text": "During its mission, it can even transmit"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 714871.0,
      "end_time": 718834.0,
      "text": "a live video feed back to a ground station laptop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 718834.0,
      "end_time": 720377.0,
      "text": "which allows the user"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 720377.0,
      "end_time": 723307.0,
      "text": "to see what the drone is seeing in real time."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 723307.0,
      "end_time": 725729.0,
      "text": "It carries a variety of sensors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 725729.0,
      "end_time": 728067.0,
      "text": "and the photo quality of some of these sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 728067.0,
      "end_time": 732277.0,
      "text": "can be as high as one to two centimeters per pixel."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 732277.0,
      "end_time": 735958.0,
      "text": "This drone can stay in the air for 40 to 60 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 735958.0,
      "end_time": 739082.0,
      "text": "which gives it a range of up to 50 kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 739082.0,
      "end_time": 740997.0,
      "text": "That is quite sufficient for most"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 740997.0,
      "end_time": 743996.0,
      "text": "of our conservation applications."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 743996.0,
      "end_time": 746066.0,
      "text": "Now, conservation drones began as"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 746066.0,
      "end_time": 748257.0,
      "text": "a crazy idea from two biologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 748257.0,
      "end_time": 751542.0,
      "text": "who are just deeply passionate about this technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 751542.0,
      "end_time": 753692.0,
      "text": "And we believe, strongly believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 753692.0,
      "end_time": 757039.0,
      "text": "that drones can and will be a game changer"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 757039.0,
      "end_time": 760073.0,
      "text": "for conservation research and applications."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 760073.0,
      "end_time": 763248.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve had our fair share of skeptics and critics"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 763248.0,
      "end_time": 766769.0,
      "text": "who thought that we were just fooling around with toy planes."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 766769.0,
      "end_time": 768195.0,
      "text": "And in a way, they are right."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 768195.0,
      "end_time": 769824.0,
      "text": "I mean, let&#39;s be honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 769824.0,
      "end_time": 773512.0,
      "text": "drones are the ultimate toys for boys."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 773512.0,
      "end_time": 775918.0,
      "text": "But at the same time, we&#39;ve also gotten to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 775918.0,
      "end_time": 778167.0,
      "text": "many wonderful colleagues and collaborators"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 778167.0,
      "end_time": 779715.0,
      "text": "who share our vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 779715.0,
      "end_time": 782571.0,
      "text": "and see the potential of conservation drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 782571.0,
      "end_time": 786170.0,
      "text": "To us, it is obvious that conservation biologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 786170.0,
      "end_time": 788428.0,
      "text": "and practitioners should make full use"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 788428.0,
      "end_time": 791962.0,
      "text": "of every available tool, including drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 791962.0,
      "end_time": 794603.0,
      "text": "in our fight to save the last remaining forests"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 794603.0,
      "end_time": 796390.0,
      "text": "and wildlife of this planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 796390.0,
      "end_time": 798388.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 798388.0,
      "end_time": 808388.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}